    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1581 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 3 0 -1 15845 0 0}{f 5 21 1 201}Hurry, hurry, hurry! You can talk later![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1581 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 5 21 1 201}Hurry up and get to your rooms. I don't want to get yelled at for your behavior![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1581 4 -1 -1 0 0}{f 5 21 1 201}Yes? Do you not know which room you're in?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
